(346, '_transient_dash_88ae138922fe95674369b1cb3d215a2b', '<div class="rss-widget"><ul><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''https://wordpress.org/news/2015/12/clifford/''>WordPress 4.4 “Clifford”</a> <span class="rss-date">December 8, 2015</span><div class="rssSummary">Version 4.4 of WordPress, named “Clifford” in honor of jazz trumpeter Clifford Brown, is available for download or update in your WordPress dashboard. New features in 4.4 make your site more connected and responsive. Clifford also introduces a new default theme, Twenty Sixteen. Introducing Twenty Sixteen Our newest default theme, Twenty Sixteen, is a modern take [&hellip;]</div></li></ul></div><div class="rss-widget"><ul><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''http://wptavern.com/drupal-community-considering-a-decoupled-architecture''>WPTavern: Drupal Community Considering a Decoupled Architecture</a></li><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''http://wptavern.com/how-to-fix-images-not-loading-in-wordpress-4-4-while-using-ssl''>WPTavern: How to Fix Images Not Loading in WordPress 4.4 While Using SSL</a></li><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''http://wptavern.com/help-edward-caissies-wife-receive-medical-treatment-and-equipment''>WPTavern: Help Edward Caissie’s Wife Receive Medical Treatment and Equipment</a></li></ul></div><div class="rss-widget"><ul><li class=''dashboard-news-plugin''><span>Popular Plugin:</span> <a href=''https://wordpress.org/plugins/updraftplus/'' class=''dashboard-news-plugin-link''>UpdraftPlus Backup and Restoration</a>&nbsp;<span>(<a href=''plugin-install.php?tab=plugin-information&amp;plugin=updraftplus&amp;_wpnonce=f6592a52c9&amp;TB_iframe=true&amp;width=600&amp;height=800'' class=''thickbox'' title=''UpdraftPlus Backup and Restoration''>Install</a>)</span></li></ul></div>', 'no'),
