(48, 2, '2012-02-23 16:55:00', '2012-02-23 23:55:00', '<h2>A job search plan details your</h2>\n<ul>\n	<li>goals</li>\n	<li>skills</li>\n	<li>talents</li>\n	<li>education and training</li>\n	<li>companies you''ve researched</li>\n	<li>talking points for interviews</li>\n</ul>\nIn today’s business climate, you need to be open to new ways of looking for work, even if getting jobs has been easy for you up until now. You need to be focused. You need to do your homework. You must have a great resume tailored to your goal.  You need to use all methods of job hunting--agencies, newspaper ads, the Internet, social media, professional organizations, networking, and anything else you can think of to get yourself in front of the decision-makers who can hire you.\n<h2>Career Coaching Services</h2>\n<strong>Individual consulting</strong> on any aspect of the job search:\n<ul>\n	<li>choosing new options</li>\n	<li>career transition</li>\n	<li>self employment</li>\n	<li>developing a strategy</li>\n	<li>identifying your skills</li>\n	<li>researching employers</li>\n	<li>how to interview effectively</li>\n	<li>negotiating salary and benefits</li>\n</ul>\nDuring the first session, we will develop a plan based on your goals. No minimum number of hours are required.\n\n<strong>For New Mexico residents</strong>, office hours in Albuquerque for coaching are available. Call 505-235-9753 to make an appointment. Hourly rate is $45.\n\n<strong>Consulting by phone and email</strong> can be arranged on any job search topic. Hourly rate for phone or email contact is $45. Call or email to make an appointment.\n\n<strong>Coaching and Editing</strong> for fiction and nonfiction writers.  Check out my writing site at <a href="http://carolhollandmarch.com" target="_blank">Carol Holland March</a> if you are interested in writing classes or consultation on your writing.\n\n&nbsp;\n<h2>Resume Development Services</h2>\n<strong><em>Free email critique</em></strong><em> of your current document. </em>Send it to <a href="mailto:info@compassrosecareers.com">info@compassrosecareers.com</a>   Put "Critique" in the Header line.  You will receive a complimentary critique of the strengths and weaknesses of your document within 48 hours.\n\n<em><strong>If you want help writing or editing your resume</strong></em>, you can come in for a personal consultation;\n\nOR, we can talk on the phone about what you would like; OR, you can send an  email about your goals, skills, work history and education. The cost to develop a one-page resume with a covero letter is $75. Fees for a two-page resume start at $100. You will have a clearly quoted price before the work begins. Turnaround is 2-3 days.  Rush orders can be accommodated for an additional $25 fee.\n\n<strong>Cover Letters and Follow-up Letters</strong> are a MUST if you want to be successful. Letters can be written for specific jobs or you can order a basic letter about your skills and experience that you can tailor to different jobs on your own.\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<em>To ask a question, make a comment, request services or send a resume for evaluation, you can use the form below. </em>\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<form action="/webformmailer.php" method="post"><input type="hidden" name="subject" value="Submission" /> <input type="hidden" name="redirect" value="thankyou.html" /> First Name:\n<input type="text" name="FirstName" /> Last Name :\n<input type="text" name="LastName" /> Email:\n<input type="text" name="email" /> Comments:\n<textarea cols="40" name="comments" rows="10">Type comments here.</textarea> <input type="submit" name="submit" value="submit" /> <input type="hidden" name="form_order" value="alpha" /> <input type="hidden" name="form_delivery" value="hourly_digest" /> <input type="hidden" name="form_format" value="html" /></form>', 'Services', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'contact-2', '', '', '2012-02-23 16:55:00', '2012-02-23 23:55:00', '', 0, 'http://compassrosecareers.com/?page_id=46', 3, 'page', '', 0),
(55, 2, '2012-02-23 17:08:49', '2012-02-24 00:08:49', '<h2>Find a job easily and faster with a great resume</h2>\n<ul>\n	<li>A great resume shows who you are, what you can do, and what you offer an employer</li>\n	<li>A great resume puts you in front of the ones who can hire you</li>\n	<li>A great resume reduces the time it takes to find that new job</li>\n</ul>\nFor a personalized, professional resume that will sell you to recruiters and hiring managers, let us craft a document that will show you at your finest.  All resumes are customized to your experience, skills, and preferences. We are not finished until you are satisfied.\n\nWe are experienced with new graduates, managers,educators, technical, artists, administrators, and health and science occupations. Our work is of the highest quality and tailored to your background and needs.\n<h1>1-Page Resume/Cover letter is only $75</h1>\n<h2>Longer resumes for those with more work experience start at $100.00.</h2>\n<h2>Your satisfaction is guaranteed.</h2>\n<h2>Free email critique of your current document.<em> </em></h2>\n<em></em>For your free no-obligation critique, Send your document  to <a href="mailto:info@compassrosecareers.com">info@compassrosecareers.com</a>   Put "Critique" in the Header line.  You will receive ascomplimentary critique of the strengths and weaknesses of your document within 48 hours\n<h2> Or call 505-235-9753</h2>\n&nbsp;', 'Welcome to Compass Rose Careers', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'welcome-2', '', '', '2012-02-23 17:08:49', '2012-02-24 00:08:49', '', 0, 'http://compassrosecareers.com/?page_id=55', 15, 'page', '', 0),
