(396, 2, '2013-02-11 16:44:06', '2013-02-11 23:44:06', 'Here are some places where jobs are listed and where you can get help with your job search\n\n<a href="http://www.dws.state.nm.us/" target="_blank">Department of Workforce Solutions</a> - job listings, free computers and faxes, training, resources\n501 Mountain NE, 501 Mountain Rd NE\nAlbuquerque, NM 87103\nPhone: 505-843-1900\nFax: 505-843-1991\n\nFederal Job Opportunities - <a href="https://help.usajobs.gov/index.php/Main_Page">USAJobs.gov</a>\n\nNew Mexico State Personnel Board - <a href="http://www.dws.state.nm.us/" target="_blank">State civil service jobs </a>\n\nCity of Albuquerque <a href="http://www.cabq.gov/jobs/">civil service jobs </a>\n\n&nbsp;', 'Resources for Job Seekers', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'resources-for-job-seekers', '', '', '2013-02-11 16:44:06', '2013-02-11 23:44:06', '', 0, 'http://compassrosecareers.com/?page_id=396', 5, 'page', '', 0),
